videos.headline: Brossette goes 50 yards untouched for TD
videos.description: LSU RB Nick Brossette takes the handoff, finds the open lane and cruises 50 yards into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Bandy ejected for targeting in first quarter
videos.description: Miami CB Trajan Bandy gets ejected for helmet-to-helmet contact with LSU's Dee Anderson, forcing a fumble the Tigers recovered.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bandy ejected for targeting in first quarter) 2018/09/02

videos.headline: Miami's Thomas makes incredible one-handed grab
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier tosses a 16-yard pass to WR Jeff Thomas, who hauls in the grab with one hand.

videos.headline: Brossette makes nice cut for second TD
videos.description: LSU RB Nick Brossette makes a nice cut to find the open lane and walk into the end zone for a 1-yard score, his second touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: LSU's Phillips takes INT to the house
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier's pass goes right into the hands of LSU LB Jacob Phillips, who returns the interception 45 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU dominating Miami at the half
videos.description: After a pre-game scuffle ensued between LSU and Miami, the Tigers get two touchdowns from Nick Brossette and a pick-6 to lead 27-3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (LSU dominating Miami at the half) 2018/09/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LSU's Battle jukes multiple defenders on INT return
videos.description: LSU safety John Battle picks off Malik Rosier and returns it 29 yards while side-stepping multiple defenders.

videos.headline: Miami's Thomas just keeps a foot inbounds on leaping catch
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier tosses a 32-yard pass towards the sideline to WR Jeff Thomas, who makes a jumping catch while keeping one foot inbounds.

videos.headline: Rosier keeps it himself for Miami's first TD
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier keeps the ball himself and walks into the end zone untouched for Miami's first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Hightower leaps above defender for Miami TD
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier lofts a 32-yard pass towards the end zone and WR Brian Hightower makes a leaping catch over a defender for the touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU's Fehoko sacks Rosier on 4th down
videos.description: Hurricanes QB Malik Rosier drops back to pass, but gets sacked by LSU DE Breiden Fehoko, forcing a turnover on downs.

videos.headline: LSU's Burrow says he wanted to execute at a high level
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow explains how he was able lead the team past Miami on Sunday night and how talented the Tigers can be moving forward.

videos.headline: Orgeron pleased with Burrow's performance in win
videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron expresses his thoughts on the performances of  QB Joe Burrow and RB Nick Brossette in the Tigers' win.

videos.headline: LSU too much for Miami
videos.description: After a testy pregame scuffle, the Tigers jump out to a huge lead courtesy of two Nick Brossette touchdowns and win 33-17.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (LSU too much for Miami) 2018/09/02 ESHEET
